WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 33=

00:01:39.090 --> 00:01:39.980 line:80%
Make way.

00:01:45.010 --> 00:01:45.850 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:01:46.700 --> 00:01:47.730 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:01:47.730 --> 00:01:49.010 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:01:49.010 --> 00:01:52.540 line:80%
the Young Master came here to propose.

00:01:54.780 --> 00:01:55.650 line:80%
Two years apart,

00:01:55.650 --> 00:01:56.570 line:80%
Manager Zhao

00:01:56.570 --> 00:01:57.850 line:80%
has become impressive.

00:01:57.850 --> 00:01:58.850 line:80%
She brought two men back.

00:01:59.180 --> 00:02:00.130 line:80%
Impressive.

00:02:00.130 --> 00:02:01.820 line:80%
As expected of the manager.

00:02:03.730 --> 00:02:04.570 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:02:05.010 --> 00:02:07.180 line:80%
Zhao was just confined over you,

00:02:07.180 --> 00:02:08.583 line:80%
and you came so openly.

00:02:08.594 --> 00:02:10.274 line:80%
You're putting her
in an awkward position.

00:02:10.810 --> 00:02:12.300 line:80%
Please, go back.

00:02:12.300 --> 00:02:14.180 line:80%
Don't provoke a sect conflict.

00:02:14.460 --> 00:02:15.370 line:80%
Mr. Song,

00:02:15.930 --> 00:02:17.410 line:80%
I think what you just said

00:02:17.780 --> 00:02:20.060 line:80%
was biased and narrow-minded.

00:02:20.460 --> 00:02:22.020 line:80%
What's wrong with a man

00:02:22.020 --> 00:02:23.490 line:80%
proposing to an unmarried woman

00:02:23.490 --> 00:02:26.060 line:80%
openly and honorably?

00:02:26.580 --> 00:02:27.460 line:80%
Besides,

00:02:27.460 --> 00:02:29.210 line:80%
we came with sincerity.

00:02:29.210 --> 00:02:31.140 line:80%
The Young Master is charming,

00:02:31.140 --> 00:02:32.300 line:80%
handsome,

00:02:32.300 --> 00:02:34.210 line:80%
wealthy, and well-mannered.

00:02:34.210 --> 00:02:35.620 line:80%
He's a martial arts prodigy.

00:02:35.620 --> 00:02:36.650 line:80%
Everyone,

00:02:36.650 --> 00:02:38.580 line:80%
does he match Miss Cai?

00:02:38.580 --> 00:02:40.370 line:80%
Perfect match.

00:02:44.410 --> 00:02:45.410 line:80%
Mr. Song,

00:02:45.410 --> 00:02:46.690 line:80%
are you afraid

00:02:46.690 --> 00:02:48.410 line:80%
you can't beat the Young Master,

00:02:49.060 --> 00:02:50.410 line:80%
so you won't let us in?

00:02:51.930 --> 00:02:53.060 line:80%
Everyone, please leave.

00:02:58.300 --> 00:02:59.140 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:02:59.490 --> 00:03:00.620 line:80%
may we speak privately?

00:03:02.090 --> 00:03:03.140 line:80%
What do you want?

00:03:04.210 --> 00:03:05.970 line:80%
Luoying Valley
no longer has what you want.

00:03:06.410 --> 00:03:07.250 line:80%
But you are here.

00:03:09.210 --> 00:03:10.460 line:80%
If I hadn't come,

00:03:11.020 --> 00:03:11.933 line:80%
would I soon receive

00:03:11.944 --> 00:03:13.524 line:80%
your wedding invitation with Song Yuzhi?

00:03:18.530 --> 00:03:19.370 line:80%
Be serious.

00:03:20.340 --> 00:03:21.180 line:80%
The Guangtian matter

00:03:21.860 --> 00:03:23.090 line:80%
is led by the man in black.

00:03:23.810 --> 00:03:26.300 line:80%
He used corpse slaves
to frame Song Shijun,

00:03:26.970 --> 00:03:28.340 line:80%
obviously reckless,

00:03:29.090 --> 00:03:30.370 line:80%
planning a final strike.

00:03:31.020 --> 00:03:32.930 line:80%
We must lure him out

00:03:33.340 --> 00:03:34.300 line:80%
before his next move.

00:03:35.340 --> 00:03:36.180 line:80%
How?

00:03:36.740 --> 00:03:38.300 line:80%
They slaughtered the Chang clan

00:03:38.690 --> 00:03:40.020 line:80%
for the Jade Sunflower.

00:03:41.020 --> 00:03:42.780 line:80%
Later, each step

00:03:42.780 --> 00:03:44.410 line:80%
was tied to it.

00:03:44.930 --> 00:03:46.090 line:80%
I've spread the word

00:03:46.350 --> 00:03:47.210 line:80%
that the treasure

00:03:47.210 --> 00:03:48.780 line:80%
is in my father's relics.

00:03:49.210 --> 00:03:50.410 line:80%
I'll use it as a betrothal gift

00:03:51.140 --> 00:03:52.060 line:80%
to marry you.

00:03:53.690 --> 00:03:55.090 line:80%
Guess if the man in black

00:03:56.300 --> 00:03:57.410 line:80%
will check it out.

00:03:58.090 --> 00:04:00.326 line:80%
If they also seek the Ziwei Method,

00:04:00.337 --> 00:04:02.023 line:80%
they must know
the Night Orchid is ruined.

00:04:02.210 --> 00:04:03.410 line:80%
How can you be sure

00:04:03.410 --> 00:04:05.370 line:80%
they'd still care
about the Jade Sunflower?

00:04:06.740 --> 00:04:07.780 line:80%
Worth a try.

00:04:27.900 --> 00:04:29.530 line:80%
You're not really here to propose.

00:04:30.380 --> 00:04:31.460 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:04:31.460 --> 00:04:33.050 line:80%
why bring so many gifts?

00:04:33.500 --> 00:04:34.780 line:80%
It's my first visit.

00:04:35.410 --> 00:04:36.730 line:80%
I should bring meeting gifts.

00:04:39.580 --> 00:04:40.820 line:80%
This Shennong Toxin

00:04:41.210 --> 00:04:42.610 line:80%
is said to be the king of poisons.

00:04:42.940 --> 00:04:43.780 line:80%
Only one bottle

00:04:44.290 --> 00:04:45.130 line:80%
in the world.

00:04:46.170 --> 00:04:49.380 line:80%
It really exists!

00:04:49.380 --> 00:04:50.820 line:80%
Restrain yourself.

00:04:56.720 --> 00:04:57.570 line:80%
The king of poisons.

00:04:57.570 --> 00:04:58.900 line:80%
Most toxic!

00:05:01.290 --> 00:05:02.130 line:80%
Lord Cai,

00:05:03.210 --> 00:05:04.050 line:80%
look at this.

00:05:05.050 --> 00:05:05.970 line:80%
A dragon hook.

00:05:06.340 --> 00:05:08.210 line:80%
I heard you enjoy fishing

00:05:08.210 --> 00:05:09.210 line:80%
in your spare time.

00:05:09.530 --> 00:05:11.210 line:80%
I hope you like it.

00:05:11.700 --> 00:05:12.540 line:80%
Of course.

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:14.650 line:80%
You know so much.

00:05:14.650 --> 00:05:15.900 line:80%
It's fun!

00:05:16.380 --> 00:05:17.970 line:80%
Flying so high!

00:05:17.970 --> 00:05:20.140 line:80%
Flying high!

00:05:22.850 --> 00:05:23.690 line:80%
Cai Han.

00:05:24.940 --> 00:05:25.780 line:80%
Ning,

00:05:26.020 --> 00:05:28.380 line:80%
can you come here often?

00:05:28.380 --> 00:05:29.730 line:80%
I like you so much!

00:05:31.210 --> 00:05:32.050 line:80%
Sure.

00:05:33.110 --> 00:05:33.970 line:80%
It's the real...

00:05:33.970 --> 00:05:35.700 line:80%
Then I'll visit often.

00:05:35.700 --> 00:05:36.700 line:80%
Every visit,

00:05:36.700 --> 00:05:38.210 line:80%
I'll bring lots of fun things, okay?

00:05:38.210 --> 00:05:39.210 line:80%
Yes!

00:05:39.780 --> 00:05:40.620 line:80%
Stop it.

00:05:41.340 --> 00:05:42.940 line:80%
You came from afar.

00:05:43.290 --> 00:05:44.170 line:80%
You must be exhausted.

00:05:44.820 --> 00:05:46.410 line:80%
Zhao,

00:05:46.410 --> 00:05:48.290 line:80%
take Mr. Mu to rest.

00:05:48.730 --> 00:05:49.570 line:80%
Let's go.

00:05:50.410 --> 00:05:51.250 line:80%
Hold me.

00:05:53.610 --> 00:05:54.460 line:80%
Cai Han.

00:05:54.460 --> 00:05:55.410 line:80%
Okay, I'll hold you.

00:05:56.460 --> 00:05:57.300 line:80%
Let's go.

00:05:57.850 --> 00:06:00.850 line:80%
Flying high!

00:06:03.530 --> 00:06:04.780 line:80%
So, this is your chamber.

00:06:06.140 --> 00:06:07.900 line:80%
It looks so...

00:06:09.210 --> 00:06:10.050 line:80%
red.

00:06:10.730 --> 00:06:11.900 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:06:12.210 --> 00:06:13.050 line:80%
I like it.

00:06:14.530 --> 00:06:15.650 line:80%
I like it too.

00:06:16.889 --> 00:06:18.848 line:80%
What kind of place do you think
I should live in?

00:06:19.530 --> 00:06:20.940 line:80%
I think it should be

00:06:20.940 --> 00:06:22.090 line:80%
a place with flowers,

00:06:22.610 --> 00:06:23.820 line:80%
cats, and dogs,

00:06:25.050 --> 00:06:25.900 line:80%
bustling and lively.

00:06:27.730 --> 00:06:28.580 line:80%
Aunt was injured.

00:06:28.900 --> 00:06:30.500 line:80%
I couldn't have pets.

00:06:31.460 --> 00:06:32.610 line:80%
This is my home.

00:06:33.340 --> 00:06:34.380 line:80%
It was also Aunt's home.

00:06:35.090 --> 00:06:36.900 line:80%
I'd lived with her since childhood.

00:06:43.140 --> 00:06:44.820 line:80%
(Spring and Blossoms)

00:06:48.140 --> 00:06:49.580 line:80%
Aunt doesn't like makeup,

00:06:49.970 --> 00:06:51.780 line:80%
but to cover the bitter smell,

00:06:52.970 --> 00:06:54.380 line:80%
I buy scented cakes

00:06:54.730 --> 00:06:55.580 line:80%
to scent the room.

00:06:56.170 --> 00:06:57.730 line:80%
This way, Aunt could always smell

00:06:58.020 --> 00:07:00.140 line:80%
the four seasons of Luoying Valley.

00:07:00.900 --> 00:07:01.740 line:80%
Speaking of which,

00:07:02.820 --> 00:07:04.340 line:80%
I respect my father,

00:07:05.410 --> 00:07:06.530 line:80%
but I admire

00:07:07.020 --> 00:07:08.020 line:80%
your aunt most.

00:07:08.970 --> 00:07:10.140 line:80%
As a woman,

00:07:10.900 --> 00:07:11.780 line:80%
she truly controlled

00:07:11.780 --> 00:07:13.090 line:80%
her life.

00:07:13.700 --> 00:07:15.730 line:80%
As she wanted, she wandered Jianghu

00:07:16.170 --> 00:07:18.290 line:80%
and slew the fiend.

00:07:18.970 --> 00:07:19.850 line:80%
Truly

00:07:20.970 --> 00:07:21.940 line:80%
free as wind and fire.

00:07:22.500 --> 00:07:23.820 line:80%
Aunt told me

00:07:24.290 --> 00:07:25.850 line:80%
she was satisfied with her life.

00:07:26.500 --> 00:07:28.460 line:80%
Compared to the fame as a heroine,

00:07:29.210 --> 00:07:31.290 line:80%
wandering

00:07:32.210 --> 00:07:33.940 line:80%
with like-minded friends,

00:07:34.380 --> 00:07:35.500 line:80%
doing good,

00:07:35.780 --> 00:07:36.650 line:80%
sharing life and death

00:07:37.410 --> 00:07:38.490 line:80%
made her freer and happier.

00:07:38.700 --> 00:07:39.610 line:80%
Like

00:07:40.210 --> 00:07:41.050 line:80%
Mr. Chang

00:07:41.820 --> 00:07:42.660 line:80%
and Lord Qi?

00:07:42.970 --> 00:07:46.050 line:80%
When Nie Hengcheng's disciples
sought revenge here,

00:07:46.610 --> 00:07:48.380 line:80%
Uncle Chang and Master

00:07:48.820 --> 00:07:50.290 line:80%
protected our family.

00:08:30.340 --> 00:08:34.220 line:80%
(Spring and Blossoms)

00:08:38.330 --> 00:08:39.740 line:80%
It's okay. Be good.

00:08:47.620 --> 00:08:49.780 line:80%
You are the Nanny Chang Aunt spoke of?

00:08:52.020 --> 00:08:52.860 line:80%
Yes.

00:08:53.050 --> 00:08:54.140 line:80%
That's him.

00:09:00.170 --> 00:09:01.140 line:80%
Later,

00:09:01.140 --> 00:09:02.220 line:80%
Aunt fell ill,

00:09:02.220 --> 00:09:03.330 line:80%
avoiding outsiders.

00:09:04.500 --> 00:09:06.140 line:80%
Uncle Zhou's father was sick

00:09:06.140 --> 00:09:07.100 line:80%
and seldom visited.

00:09:07.690 --> 00:09:09.020 line:80%
Uncle Chang retired.

00:09:09.620 --> 00:09:10.460 line:80%
But Master

00:09:11.050 --> 00:09:12.140 line:80%
came every year.

00:09:12.740 --> 00:09:14.530 line:80%
Besides Aunt and my parents,

00:09:14.530 --> 00:09:16.410 line:80%
he's the one I saw most often.

00:09:18.170 --> 00:09:19.050 line:80%
Lord Qi

00:09:20.410 --> 00:09:21.900 line:80%
came to heal Ms. Cai?

00:09:24.170 --> 00:09:25.380 line:80%
The Disintegration

00:09:25.810 --> 00:09:26.780 line:80%
cut all her meridians.

00:09:27.930 --> 00:09:28.980 line:80%
For decades,

00:09:29.530 --> 00:09:30.690 line:80%
Master used

00:09:30.690 --> 00:09:32.020 line:80%
Tianhuo Dragon Aura

00:09:32.020 --> 00:09:33.290 line:80%
to sustain Aunt's life.

00:09:33.860 --> 00:09:34.700 line:80%
Every year,

00:09:35.140 --> 00:09:36.290 line:80%
Master stayed

00:09:36.290 --> 00:09:37.130 line:80%
for a month.

00:09:37.810 --> 00:09:38.650 line:80%
In that month,

00:09:38.930 --> 00:09:41.170 line:80%
he expended energy every day

00:09:41.650 --> 00:09:42.860 line:80%
to heal Aunt.

00:09:43.250 --> 00:09:44.556 line:80%
Master's talent is extraordinary,

00:09:44.900 --> 00:09:46.570 line:80%
but martial arts lag

00:09:47.020 --> 00:09:48.140 line:80%
due to this.

00:09:48.650 --> 00:09:49.972 line:80%
Otherwise, how could Qiu Yuanfeng

00:09:49.983 --> 00:09:52.020 line:80%
act so arrogantly at the memorial?

00:09:55.050 --> 00:09:58.450 line:80%
Lord Qi truly cares for Ms. Cai.

00:09:58.860 --> 00:09:59.810 line:80%
Back then,

00:09:59.810 --> 00:10:02.220 line:80%
he must've known Yin Dai's deeds,

00:10:03.050 --> 00:10:04.530 line:80%
watching the Yin clan prosper

00:10:04.980 --> 00:10:06.380 line:80%
while caring for Ms. Cai

00:10:07.050 --> 00:10:08.100 line:80%
in her sickbed.

00:10:08.620 --> 00:10:09.460 line:80%
It must've

00:10:10.620 --> 00:10:11.860 line:80%
pained him deeply.

00:10:22.740 --> 00:10:23.580 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:10:25.980 --> 00:10:26.820 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:10:27.650 --> 00:10:28.690 line:80%
You suffer here,

00:10:29.020 --> 00:10:30.220 line:80%
yet they live freely,

00:10:31.140 --> 00:10:32.026 line:80%
forgetting everything.

00:10:32.330 --> 00:10:33.170 line:80%
It's fine.

00:10:34.620 --> 00:10:35.570 line:80%
It doesn't matter

00:10:36.410 --> 00:10:37.450 line:80%
if someone

00:10:38.100 --> 00:10:39.740 line:80%
remembers.

00:10:40.620 --> 00:10:42.410 line:80%
Peace of mind is more important

00:10:42.410 --> 00:10:44.140 line:80%
than right or wrong.

00:10:44.900 --> 00:10:46.620 line:80%
Of course, right and wrong matter.

00:10:46.620 --> 00:10:47.500 line:80%
Mother said

00:10:47.500 --> 00:10:48.780 line:80%
that in life,

00:10:48.780 --> 00:10:50.170 line:80%
we should

00:10:50.170 --> 00:10:51.530 line:80%
take revenge.

00:10:51.930 --> 00:10:53.170 line:80%
Take medicine, Aunt.

00:10:54.410 --> 00:10:55.250 line:80%
Sure.

00:11:01.780 --> 00:11:03.690 line:80%
But the saddest thing

00:11:05.220 --> 00:11:07.380 line:80%
is letting hatred cloud your mind,

00:11:08.690 --> 00:11:10.570 line:80%
ruining your own life.

00:11:11.930 --> 00:11:13.020 line:80%
That would only cause

00:11:13.690 --> 00:11:14.790 line:80%
the ones you love to suffer

00:11:15.117 --> 00:11:16.410 line:80%
and the ones you hate to rejoice.

00:11:21.330 --> 00:11:22.410 line:80%
Even if Master was sad,

00:11:22.410 --> 00:11:23.410 line:80%
he wouldn't say anything.

00:11:23.930 --> 00:11:25.290 line:80%
He's a good man.

00:11:25.860 --> 00:11:27.690 line:80%
When I was small,
swinging a silver chain,

00:11:27.690 --> 00:11:28.900 line:80%
I hurt my hand.

00:11:29.530 --> 00:11:31.290 line:80%
Master immediately carried me

00:11:31.650 --> 00:11:32.740 line:80%
to complain to Aunt,

00:11:33.100 --> 00:11:35.100 line:80%
asking why I started
martial arts so early.

00:11:35.810 --> 00:11:37.650 line:80%
Aunt laughed at him for fussing,

00:11:38.330 --> 00:11:39.650 line:80%
so unlike a lord.

00:11:40.290 --> 00:11:41.500 line:80%
Yet after all these years,

00:11:41.500 --> 00:11:43.810 line:80%
he still firmly holds his position.

00:11:46.500 --> 00:11:47.340 line:80%
Enough.

00:11:48.100 --> 00:11:49.570 line:80%
Your room is upstairs.

00:11:49.570 --> 00:11:50.780 line:80%
Young Master, rest.

00:11:54.810 --> 00:11:56.020 line:80%
If I stay upstairs,

00:11:58.020 --> 00:11:59.020 line:80%
what about Song Yuzhi?

00:12:00.020 --> 00:12:00.926 line:80%
He stays upstairs too.

00:12:27.220 --> 00:12:28.060 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:12:29.290 --> 00:12:30.130 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:12:31.020 --> 00:12:31.860 line:80%
Father.

00:12:35.980 --> 00:12:36.930 line:80%
Guangtian Sect...

00:12:37.450 --> 00:12:38.290 line:80%
Guangtian Sect...

00:12:38.650 --> 00:12:40.500 line:80%
Uncle Pang has contacted old members.

00:12:40.500 --> 00:12:41.500 line:80%
News will come soon.

00:12:41.780 --> 00:12:42.900 line:80%
Father, don't worry.

00:12:43.930 --> 00:12:44.770 line:80%
Father,

00:12:45.140 --> 00:12:46.410 line:80%
who attacked you

00:12:46.780 --> 00:12:48.220 line:80%
and planted the Puppet Gu?

00:12:52.410 --> 00:12:53.250 line:80%
Xiuzhi,

00:12:55.170 --> 00:12:57.330 line:80%
why did you suddenly go to Siqi Sect

00:12:57.330 --> 00:12:58.290 line:80%
the other day?

00:13:02.690 --> 00:13:03.620 line:80%
Song Xiuzhi,

00:13:04.100 --> 00:13:05.450 line:80%
I'm talking to you.

00:13:16.500 --> 00:13:17.860 line:80%
Only a few people

00:13:18.930 --> 00:13:20.410 line:80%
can hurt you with a palm.

00:13:21.450 --> 00:13:22.620 line:80%
Not Zhou Zhizhen.

00:13:24.020 --> 00:13:27.220 line:80%
I recognize his internal power.

00:13:27.650 --> 00:13:28.740 line:80%
Could it be...

00:13:35.170 --> 00:13:36.020 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:13:37.620 --> 00:13:39.620 line:80%
the Six Sects are about to change.

00:13:40.500 --> 00:13:42.500 line:80%
But I'm now useless.

00:13:43.410 --> 00:13:44.860 line:80%
I can't protect you.

00:13:45.620 --> 00:13:47.410 line:80%
Better stay in Luoying Valley.

00:13:47.780 --> 00:13:49.330 line:80%
- Zhao...
- Zhao is my junior sister.

00:13:50.980 --> 00:13:51.820 line:80%
She'll only be

00:13:52.930 --> 00:13:54.330 line:80%
my junior sister.

00:13:55.380 --> 00:13:57.050 line:80%
The priority is to recover power.

00:13:57.570 --> 00:13:58.410 line:80%
A hard battle

00:13:58.980 --> 00:14:00.330 line:80%
is inevitable.

00:14:01.690 --> 00:14:02.530 line:80%
Good.

00:14:03.100 --> 00:14:04.530 line:80%
Since you've figured it out,

00:14:05.020 --> 00:14:06.100 line:80%
I'll stop talking.

00:14:07.620 --> 00:14:09.100 line:80%
After this, the world

00:14:10.450 --> 00:14:13.220 line:80%
is full of opportunity.

00:14:15.810 --> 00:14:16.930 line:80%
Lord Cai said

00:14:16.930 --> 00:14:17.930 line:80%
I'm a guest.

00:14:17.930 --> 00:14:19.810 line:80%
So, you should show me around.

00:14:22.100 --> 00:14:23.690 line:80%
The braised meat shop ahead

00:14:24.020 --> 00:14:25.860 line:80%
has perfected its broth
for three generations.

00:14:26.100 --> 00:14:27.966 line:80%
(Braised)
Even a shoe sole smells great in it.

00:14:29.140 --> 00:14:30.290 line:80%
The perfume shop

00:14:30.690 --> 00:14:32.650 line:80%
(Yulan Scent)
uses the freshest flowers,

00:14:33.100 --> 00:14:35.170 line:80%
steaming, drying, grinding, and mixing.

00:14:35.650 --> 00:14:37.380 line:80%
My scented cakes are all from there.

00:14:38.930 --> 00:14:41.170 line:80%
(Spring Tofu Pudding)
This is the Spring Tofu Pudding.

00:14:45.100 --> 00:14:46.570 line:80%
You must be Uncle Douhua.

00:14:49.410 --> 00:14:50.250 line:80%
Why?

00:14:50.570 --> 00:14:51.570 line:80%
You know me?

00:14:51.570 --> 00:14:53.050 line:80%
Zhao often mentions you.

00:14:53.690 --> 00:14:54.980 line:80%
Your tofu pudding

00:14:54.980 --> 00:14:56.220 line:80%
is praised endlessly.

00:14:57.930 --> 00:14:58.810 line:80%
Stop talking.

00:14:58.810 --> 00:14:59.980 line:80%
Try a bowl.

00:15:00.450 --> 00:15:01.380 line:80%
Sure.

00:15:01.380 --> 00:15:02.220 line:80%
Here, sit.

00:15:05.900 --> 00:15:06.860 line:80%
Here.

00:15:07.900 --> 00:15:09.140 line:80%
We were shopping.

00:15:09.140 --> 00:15:10.020 line:80%
Why eat?

00:15:10.570 --> 00:15:11.410 line:80%
Manager.

00:15:16.220 --> 00:15:17.060 line:80%
How is it?

00:15:17.690 --> 00:15:18.690 line:80%
This tofu pudding

00:15:19.020 --> 00:15:19.930 line:80%
is soft yet firm

00:15:19.930 --> 00:15:21.140 line:80%
and tender yet rich.

00:15:21.140 --> 00:15:21.980 line:80%
Delicious!

00:15:22.380 --> 00:15:23.900 line:80%
Good, eat more if you like.

00:15:24.330 --> 00:15:25.170 line:80%
Manager,

00:15:25.170 --> 00:15:26.690 line:80%
you eat; I'll go inside.

00:15:35.650 --> 00:15:37.020 line:80%
I heard that 18 years ago,

00:15:37.570 --> 00:15:39.410 line:80%
a notorious thief roamed Jiangbei.

00:15:40.020 --> 00:15:41.930 line:80%
His Tai Chi was unparalleled.

00:15:42.620 --> 00:15:44.050 line:80%
Later, he was captured by your aunt.

00:15:44.330 --> 00:15:45.170 line:80%
Unexpectedly,

00:15:45.980 --> 00:15:47.650 line:80%
using Tai Chi to grind tofu

00:15:48.900 --> 00:15:50.290 line:80%
is truly ingenious.

00:15:54.570 --> 00:15:55.690 line:80%
I always wondered

00:15:57.020 --> 00:15:59.380 line:80%
why those outlaws your aunt knew

00:15:59.900 --> 00:16:01.380 line:80%
disappeared from Jianghu.

00:16:02.810 --> 00:16:03.650 line:80%
So,

00:16:04.900 --> 00:16:06.570 line:80%
they were hiding in plain sight.

00:16:06.860 --> 00:16:07.700 line:80%
What outlaws?

00:16:08.810 --> 00:16:11.140 line:80%
They are honest businessmen.

00:16:12.290 --> 00:16:14.410 line:80%
As you know, life in Jianghu isn't easy.

00:16:14.900 --> 00:16:17.810 line:80%
Many heroes who were mighty in youth

00:16:18.170 --> 00:16:19.410 line:80%
end up injured,

00:16:19.410 --> 00:16:20.250 line:80%
ill, or old,

00:16:20.650 --> 00:16:22.100 line:80%
and their later years are bleak.

00:16:25.450 --> 00:16:26.290 line:80%
True.

00:16:27.620 --> 00:16:29.080 line:80%
In a small place like Luoying Valley,

00:16:29.740 --> 00:16:31.740 line:80%
they lived in peace for over a decade.

00:16:32.810 --> 00:16:34.450 line:80%
It must have been fate.

00:16:35.500 --> 00:16:36.810 line:80%
People have their destinies,

00:16:37.570 --> 00:16:39.020 line:80%
but it's really about temperament.

00:16:39.620 --> 00:16:40.500 line:80%
Those meant to leave

00:16:40.740 --> 00:16:41.860 line:80%
will leave.

00:16:42.570 --> 00:16:43.620 line:80%
Those who stay always have

00:16:44.780 --> 00:16:46.650 line:80%
reasons to be held back.

00:16:47.900 --> 00:16:49.140 line:80%
If they choose to remain,

00:16:49.930 --> 00:16:51.220 line:80%
there's always a reason.

00:17:04.620 --> 00:17:09.220 line:80%
(One stroke moves; Two strokes startle)

00:17:17.660 --> 00:17:18.500 line:80%
Zhao,

00:17:19.130 --> 00:17:20.810 line:80%
this place is exactly like the painting

00:17:21.660 --> 00:17:22.610 line:80%
you gave me.

00:17:24.180 --> 00:17:25.090 line:80%
I like it so much,

00:17:25.850 --> 00:17:26.850 line:80%
and I'm very pleased.

00:17:28.100 --> 00:17:30.420 line:80%
(Ingenious Study)

00:17:38.050 --> 00:17:39.220 line:80%
Is this

00:17:39.810 --> 00:17:40.890 line:80%
where Ms. Cai rests?

00:17:41.460 --> 00:17:42.500 line:80%
Before she passed,

00:17:42.890 --> 00:17:44.050 line:80%
this was her favorite place.

00:17:45.660 --> 00:17:46.780 line:80%
Before she left us,

00:17:46.780 --> 00:17:48.460 line:80%
she forbade us from making a fuss.

00:17:48.460 --> 00:17:49.500 line:80%
So,

00:17:49.500 --> 00:17:51.660 line:80%
we quietly buried her under this tree.

00:17:52.330 --> 00:17:53.170 line:80%
From then on,

00:17:53.570 --> 00:17:54.700 line:80%
she is free

00:17:55.050 --> 00:17:56.180 line:80%
under the wind and moon.

00:17:56.940 --> 00:17:58.130 line:80%
If we miss her,

00:17:58.130 --> 00:17:59.530 line:80%
we'll pour some

00:17:59.530 --> 00:18:00.890 line:80%
peach blossom wine here

00:18:01.330 --> 00:18:02.700 line:80%
during festivals.

00:18:04.570 --> 00:18:05.810 line:80%
I've dreamed of this place.

00:18:07.530 --> 00:18:09.220 line:80%
This is exactly the same as in my dream.

00:18:09.570 --> 00:18:11.220 line:80%
I dreamed that we ate tofu pudding,

00:18:12.050 --> 00:18:13.220 line:80%
picked peach blossoms,

00:18:14.050 --> 00:18:14.890 line:80%
and brewed wine.

00:18:15.660 --> 00:18:17.220 line:80%
But the Luoying Valley before my eyes

00:18:17.610 --> 00:18:19.330 line:80%
is much more beautiful than in my dream.

00:18:19.570 --> 00:18:20.410 line:80%
Perhaps

00:18:21.610 --> 00:18:23.330 line:80%
this is the place my father

00:18:25.020 --> 00:18:26.420 line:80%
longed for when he was alive.

00:18:30.500 --> 00:18:32.220 line:80%
If you like it,

00:18:33.130 --> 00:18:34.180 line:80%
you may stay here often.

00:18:36.890 --> 00:18:37.730 line:80%
Zhao,

00:18:39.220 --> 00:18:40.420 line:80%
I can marry into your family.

00:18:44.890 --> 00:18:45.890 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:18:47.130 --> 00:18:48.780 line:80%
your family is prominent.

00:18:48.780 --> 00:18:50.290 line:80%
Our Luoying Valley is small.

00:18:51.500 --> 00:18:52.850 line:80%
I can't possibly accept that.

00:18:53.980 --> 00:18:56.050 line:80%
You should think it over again.

00:18:56.050 --> 00:18:57.610 line:80%
If I can't marry into your family,

00:18:58.500 --> 00:19:00.180 line:80%
may my ashes be buried here?

00:19:01.740 --> 00:19:02.780 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:19:12.850 --> 00:19:13.690 line:80%
You failed.

00:19:14.050 --> 00:19:14.890 line:80%
Watch me.

00:19:22.570 --> 00:19:23.890 line:80%
You've grown up,

00:19:23.890 --> 00:19:25.370 line:80%
still playing marbles like a child.

00:19:25.610 --> 00:19:26.450 line:80%
Han,

00:19:26.740 --> 00:19:27.580 line:80%
you lost again.

00:19:28.180 --> 00:19:29.180 line:80%
What am I to you now?

00:19:30.370 --> 00:19:31.210 line:80%
Brother-in-law.

00:19:31.500 --> 00:19:33.090 line:80%
What? Louder.

00:19:33.090 --> 00:19:34.220 line:80%
I didn't hear you.

00:19:34.220 --> 00:19:35.850 line:80%
Brother-in-law!

00:19:37.940 --> 00:19:38.890 line:80%
Cai Han,

00:19:39.180 --> 00:19:40.570 line:80%
you sold me out for a few marbles?

00:19:40.850 --> 00:19:42.130 line:80%
Han, ignore her.

00:19:42.700 --> 00:19:43.540 line:80%
Let's continue.

00:19:44.460 --> 00:19:45.940 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:19:49.130 --> 00:19:50.180 line:80%
- See? It went in.
- Yes.

00:19:53.130 --> 00:19:54.220 line:80%
Marbles?

00:19:56.740 --> 00:19:57.580 line:80%
Marbles!

00:20:09.750 --> 00:20:10.610 line:80%
Zhao,

00:20:10.610 --> 00:20:12.330 line:80%
this isn't a marble.

00:20:12.330 --> 00:20:14.090 line:80%
It's fat and round,

00:20:14.090 --> 00:20:15.570 line:80%
rolling around.

00:20:15.570 --> 00:20:17.460 line:80%
If not a marble, what is it?

00:20:19.020 --> 00:20:20.570 line:80%
Zhao is right.

00:20:20.570 --> 00:20:21.780 line:80%
Fat, round,

00:20:21.780 --> 00:20:22.890 line:80%
and rolling.

00:20:22.890 --> 00:20:24.020 line:80%
Of course, it's a marble.

00:20:25.700 --> 00:20:26.846 line:80%
What does the Jade Sunflower

00:20:26.980 --> 00:20:28.020 line:80%
look like?

00:20:28.570 --> 00:20:30.330 line:80%
At the Li Sect's treasury,

00:20:31.180 --> 00:20:32.290 line:80%
it was burned by fire

00:20:32.850 --> 00:20:33.940 line:80%
and became blackened

00:20:34.330 --> 00:20:36.780 line:80%
and small.

00:20:38.740 --> 00:20:40.700 line:80%
Aunt brought the Jade Sunflower back.

00:20:41.153 --> 00:20:43.199 line:80%
I even played with it as a marble
when I was young.

00:20:46.050 --> 00:20:47.530 line:80%
We've searched everywhere.

00:20:47.940 --> 00:20:49.740 line:80%
Where could it be?

00:20:52.420 --> 00:20:53.850 line:80%
Did Ms. Cai

00:20:53.850 --> 00:20:55.420 line:80%
place it somewhere else?

00:20:55.980 --> 00:20:56.820 line:80%
Are you saying

00:20:57.330 --> 00:20:58.850 line:80%
Aunt entrusted it to someone else?

00:21:00.940 --> 00:21:02.090 line:80%
Zhao!

00:21:03.610 --> 00:21:04.530 line:80%
Xingjia,

00:21:05.700 --> 00:21:07.130 line:80%
is everyone settled?

00:21:07.980 --> 00:21:08.820 line:80%
Of course.

00:21:09.290 --> 00:21:11.810 line:80%
Once I got here, I heard

00:21:12.890 --> 00:21:15.610 line:80%
Mr. Mu is here to propose.

00:21:19.660 --> 00:21:21.370 line:80%
He brought plenty of gold and treasures.

00:21:23.050 --> 00:21:23.890 line:80%
Cai Han.

00:21:24.850 --> 00:21:25.690 line:80%
Why?

00:21:27.700 --> 00:21:29.260 line:80%
Enough, let's get to business.

00:21:29.570 --> 00:21:30.610 line:80%
You know what happened

00:21:31.180 --> 00:21:32.370 line:80%
to Guangtian Sect, right?

00:21:32.370 --> 00:21:34.850 line:80%
I got a pigeon message
once I returned to the sect.

00:21:35.290 --> 00:21:36.980 line:80%
Uncle Lei, worried for Yuzhi,

00:21:37.420 --> 00:21:38.420 line:80%
sent me immediately.

00:21:44.220 --> 00:21:45.850 line:80%
I may know where the Jade Sunflower is.

00:21:56.460 --> 00:21:57.740 line:80%
Cai Pingshu,

00:21:58.530 --> 00:22:00.810 line:80%
you are reckless

00:22:00.810 --> 00:22:02.290 line:80%
and ignorant,

00:22:02.290 --> 00:22:04.090 line:80%
leading all the women astray.

00:22:04.090 --> 00:22:06.180 line:80%
Utterly foolish!

00:22:11.980 --> 00:22:13.500 line:80%
I didn't say that.

00:22:13.810 --> 00:22:14.843 line:80%
Abbess Jingyuan wrote it.

00:22:15.740 --> 00:22:16.610 line:80%
What's that?

00:22:16.890 --> 00:22:18.220 line:80%
There are worse things.

00:22:18.780 --> 00:22:19.773 line:80%
Every time Aunt received

00:22:19.784 --> 00:22:21.660 line:80%
Abbess Jingyuan's pigeon letter,

00:22:21.660 --> 00:22:22.980 line:80%
she made me grind ink

00:22:22.980 --> 00:22:24.213 line:80%
and send back scolding letters.

00:22:25.500 --> 00:22:26.890 line:80%
I thought they didn't get along.

00:22:27.660 --> 00:22:28.780 line:80%
Aunt was ill for years;

00:22:29.090 --> 00:22:31.180 line:80%
Abbess Jingyuan never visited.

00:22:31.610 --> 00:22:32.450 line:80%
Now, I see.

00:22:32.660 --> 00:22:34.180 line:80%
They corresponded monthly,

00:22:34.359 --> 00:22:35.412 line:80%
closer than close friends.

00:22:35.700 --> 00:22:36.570 line:80%
You think

00:22:36.850 --> 00:22:38.610 line:80%
Ms. Cai entrusted the Jade Sunflower

00:22:38.610 --> 00:22:39.700 line:80%
to Abbess Jingyuan?

00:22:40.130 --> 00:22:41.810 line:80%
After the fire,

00:22:42.220 --> 00:22:43.290 line:80%
only the core remained.

00:22:43.850 --> 00:22:45.660 line:80%
It could be tied to a pigeon's leg.

00:22:45.660 --> 00:22:46.500 line:80%
Besides,

00:22:46.500 --> 00:22:47.500 line:80%
Abbess Jingyuan

00:22:47.500 --> 00:22:50.180 line:80%
openly opposed Aunt.

00:22:50.610 --> 00:22:51.700 line:80%
Everyone knew.

00:22:52.180 --> 00:22:53.330 line:80%
So, no one would think

00:22:53.740 --> 00:22:55.050 line:80%
the Jade Sunflower

00:22:55.050 --> 00:22:56.276 line:80%
was hidden at Xuankong Nunnery.

00:22:56.610 --> 00:22:57.780 line:80%
Why not just check?

00:22:57.980 --> 00:22:58.820 line:80%
No time to waste.

00:22:59.420 --> 00:23:00.370 line:80%
Let's go quietly.

00:23:04.660 --> 00:23:05.890 line:80%
The Jade Sunflower?

00:23:07.500 --> 00:23:08.460 line:80%
I've never heard of it.

00:23:10.940 --> 00:23:12.850 line:80%
You should reflect in Luoying Valley.

00:23:13.420 --> 00:23:15.290 line:80%
Why stir trouble here?

00:23:15.850 --> 00:23:17.850 line:80%
Back in Qingque Sect,

00:23:17.850 --> 00:23:19.570 line:80%
how did I warn you?

00:23:21.850 --> 00:23:23.660 line:80%
Why provoke the demonic sect?

00:23:24.780 --> 00:23:26.290 line:80%
I didn't provoke them.

00:23:26.290 --> 00:23:27.220 line:80%
You misunderstood.

00:23:28.130 --> 00:23:29.460 line:80%
It wasn't Zhao provoking me;

00:23:31.050 --> 00:23:32.700 line:80%
it was me provoking her.

00:23:33.610 --> 00:23:34.980 line:80%
Please, don't blame Zhao.

00:23:35.570 --> 00:23:37.290 line:80%
I'm weakened by the Nether Aura.

00:23:37.290 --> 00:23:38.700 line:80%
My core is constrained,

00:23:38.700 --> 00:23:40.330 line:80%
and I need the Sunflower to recover.

00:23:41.370 --> 00:23:42.210 line:80%
Zhao is

00:23:42.850 --> 00:23:44.020 line:80%
helping me.

00:23:44.460 --> 00:23:45.300 line:80%
Grand-aunt,

00:23:45.700 --> 00:23:47.530 line:80%
the Sunflower is too evil.

00:23:48.130 --> 00:23:50.980 line:80%
It'll bring disaster
if left in the world.

00:23:51.420 --> 00:23:52.610 line:80%
We want to find it

00:23:53.780 --> 00:23:54.740 line:80%
and destroy it.

00:24:09.610 --> 00:24:10.460 line:80%
Thank you.

00:24:25.570 --> 00:24:27.330 line:80%
It really is here.

00:24:27.810 --> 00:24:28.650 line:80%
Grand-aunt,

00:24:29.530 --> 00:24:31.890 line:80%
didn't you say you'd never heard of it?

00:24:32.850 --> 00:24:34.980 line:80%
Nuns don't lie.

00:24:35.330 --> 00:24:36.890 line:80%
I didn't lie.

00:24:37.460 --> 00:24:39.530 line:80%
Pingshu never called it

00:24:39.530 --> 00:24:40.890 line:80%
the Jade Sunflower.

00:24:41.570 --> 00:24:42.660 line:80%
I see.

00:24:43.850 --> 00:24:45.020 line:80%
Aunt said nothing,

00:24:45.530 --> 00:24:46.940 line:80%
yet you agreed to guard it.

00:24:47.940 --> 00:24:49.460 line:80%
No wonder she entrusted it

00:24:49.810 --> 00:24:51.370 line:80%
to you before dying.

00:24:53.370 --> 00:24:55.420 line:80%
She said it was important.

00:24:55.420 --> 00:24:58.180 line:80%
She worried someone would need it,

00:24:58.180 --> 00:24:59.850 line:80%
so she didn't destroy it.

00:25:00.530 --> 00:25:01.570 line:80%
She repeatedly warned me

00:25:02.050 --> 00:25:04.090 line:80%
that if it was at risk of exposure,

00:25:04.090 --> 00:25:05.530 line:80%
I should destroy it at once.

00:25:05.850 --> 00:25:06.850 line:80%
I was careless

00:25:07.330 --> 00:25:09.180 line:80%
and let it resurface.

00:25:10.370 --> 00:25:11.890 line:80%
Heal here.

00:25:28.370 --> 00:25:30.090 line:80%
I'm not sure if it will work.

00:25:30.090 --> 00:25:31.050 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:25:32.050 --> 00:25:33.890 line:80%
Pingshu used it before.

00:25:34.810 --> 00:25:36.740 line:80%
How did you know

00:25:37.850 --> 00:25:39.500 line:80%
the Jade Sunflower was here?

00:25:40.460 --> 00:25:41.610 line:80%
The pigeon.

00:25:41.610 --> 00:25:42.810 line:80%
Normally,

00:25:42.810 --> 00:25:44.056 line:80%
Luoying Valley wouldn't contact

00:25:44.780 --> 00:25:46.370 line:80%
those unfriendly to Aunt.

00:25:47.740 --> 00:25:49.090 line:80%
Only you, Grand-aunt.

00:25:49.780 --> 00:25:50.940 line:80%
Everyone knows

00:25:51.330 --> 00:25:52.530 line:80%
you dislike Aunt,

00:25:53.370 --> 00:25:54.290 line:80%
yet we had pigeons

00:25:54.890 --> 00:25:56.890 line:80%
to Xuankong Nunnery.

00:25:58.290 --> 00:25:59.660 line:80%
Xiaofeng is right.

00:26:00.220 --> 00:26:01.090 line:80%
You're clever.

00:26:01.980 --> 00:26:04.460 line:80%
If Pingshu were half as clever,

00:26:06.130 --> 00:26:08.090 line:80%
she wouldn't have died so early.

00:26:16.180 --> 00:26:17.130 line:80%
Actually,

00:26:18.090 --> 00:26:19.220 line:80%
I thought

00:26:19.940 --> 00:26:21.570 line:80%
you didn't like Aunt.

00:26:22.050 --> 00:26:23.700 line:80%
That's true.

00:26:24.570 --> 00:26:26.700 line:80%
When your mother wanted to become a nun,

00:26:27.090 --> 00:26:29.660 line:80%
she caused a commotion here,

00:26:30.090 --> 00:26:31.530 line:80%
forcing your mother back.

00:26:32.130 --> 00:26:34.050 line:80%
I dislike her wildness,

00:26:35.460 --> 00:26:36.660 line:80%
so I criticized her.

00:26:37.500 --> 00:26:38.500 line:80%
Back then,

00:26:38.500 --> 00:26:40.530 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng captured my disciples.

00:26:41.460 --> 00:26:43.050 line:80%
Only your aunt went to save them.

00:26:43.850 --> 00:26:44.690 line:80%
At that time,

00:26:45.020 --> 00:26:47.460 line:80%
several of her friends died.

00:26:47.460 --> 00:26:49.500 line:80%
- She just recovered.
- Slowly.

00:26:51.370 --> 00:26:53.010 line:80%
- Pingshu.
- Master, save us!

00:26:53.130 --> 00:26:53.980 line:80%
You're all back.

00:26:54.530 --> 00:26:55.980 line:80%
Thank you, Pingshu.

00:26:56.420 --> 00:26:57.460 line:80%
Take them back.

00:26:57.460 --> 00:26:58.700 line:80%
Leave Nie Hengcheng to me.

00:26:58.700 --> 00:26:59.540 line:80%
Alright.

00:27:00.740 --> 00:27:01.793 line:80%
In less than half a month,

00:27:02.090 --> 00:27:03.420 line:80%
she went to Mount Tu.

00:27:05.530 --> 00:27:07.850 line:80%
You know the rest.

00:27:08.570 --> 00:27:10.220 line:80%
You never went to Luoying Valley,

00:27:12.420 --> 00:27:13.660 line:80%
probably to avoid

00:27:13.660 --> 00:27:15.460 line:80%
seeing Aunt sick.

00:27:16.220 --> 00:27:17.570 line:80%
I only wanted to remember

00:27:18.610 --> 00:27:20.660 line:80%
her free-spirited self.

00:27:21.330 --> 00:27:22.530 line:80%
Because of your aunt,

00:27:23.180 --> 00:27:24.420 line:80%
many believe

00:27:24.740 --> 00:27:27.130 line:80%
a woman can stand tall too.

00:27:28.220 --> 00:27:29.290 line:80%
I recall

00:27:30.220 --> 00:27:31.220 line:80%
complaining

00:27:31.980 --> 00:27:34.290 line:80%
about you being too strict.

00:27:35.220 --> 00:27:36.810 line:80%
Aunt said

00:27:37.180 --> 00:27:38.940 line:80%
you only disliked

00:27:38.940 --> 00:27:40.780 line:80%
careless behavior,

00:27:41.610 --> 00:27:44.890 line:80%
but you were fair and unbiased.

00:27:45.810 --> 00:27:50.420 line:80%
You two were true confidantes.

00:27:56.500 --> 00:28:01.460 line:80%
(Void and Stillness)

00:28:05.810 --> 00:28:06.650 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:28:06.980 --> 00:28:07.820 line:80%
how are you?

00:28:08.020 --> 00:28:09.180 line:80%
The poison was cleared.

00:28:09.610 --> 00:28:11.180 line:80%
With some recovery, I'll be fine.

00:28:12.980 --> 00:28:13.820 line:80%
Thank you.

00:28:15.020 --> 00:28:16.050 line:80%
This object is ominous.

00:28:16.530 --> 00:28:17.610 line:80%
Destroy it soon.

00:28:17.980 --> 00:28:18.820 line:80%
Right.

00:28:19.370 --> 00:28:21.050 line:80%
It shouldn't exist in the world.

00:28:28.050 --> 00:28:29.420 line:80%
Hand over the Jade Sunflower,

00:28:29.980 --> 00:28:31.370 line:80%
or they die.

00:28:50.970 --> 00:28:51.750 line:80%
Abbess!

00:28:51.850 --> 00:28:52.690 line:80%
Abbess!

00:28:53.050 --> 00:28:53.890 line:80%
Abbess!

00:28:54.130 --> 00:28:55.330 line:80%
Zhao, take them first.

00:28:55.660 --> 00:28:56.530 line:80%
I'll handle them.

00:28:56.530 --> 00:28:57.610 line:80%
- Go.
- Go.

00:28:57.610 --> 00:28:58.450 line:80%
Go.

00:29:18.290 --> 00:29:19.890 line:80%
Mr. Chang's Willow Sword

00:29:19.890 --> 00:29:21.090 line:80%
uses entanglement as defense.

00:29:21.980 --> 00:29:22.820 line:80%
You know it,

00:29:23.610 --> 00:29:24.530 line:80%
right?

00:29:54.460 --> 00:29:55.613 line:80%
Hand over the Jade Sunflower,

00:29:55.980 --> 00:29:57.020 line:80%
or he dies.

00:30:00.370 --> 00:30:01.210 line:80%
Xingjia!

00:30:03.500 --> 00:30:04.340 line:80%
Hand it over.

00:30:07.330 --> 00:30:08.170 line:80%
Switch.

00:30:15.890 --> 00:30:16.810 line:80%
Xingjia,

00:30:16.810 --> 00:30:17.650 line:80%
are you okay?

00:30:17.810 --> 00:30:18.660 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:30:18.660 --> 00:30:19.500 line:80%
I won't die.

00:30:19.850 --> 00:30:20.740 line:80%
The Jade Sunflower!

00:30:21.050 --> 00:30:21.890 line:80%
Chase him!

00:30:22.130 --> 00:30:22.970 line:80%
It's fine.

00:30:23.250 --> 00:30:24.220 line:80%
The Night Orchid is gone.

00:30:24.220 --> 00:30:25.503 line:80%
The Jade Sunflower is of no use.

00:30:27.660 --> 00:30:28.530 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:30:29.740 --> 00:30:31.180 line:80%
They need both the Jade Sunflower

00:30:31.180 --> 00:30:33.236 line:80%
and the Night Orchid to practice.

00:30:33.250 --> 00:30:34.170 line:80%
Without both, it fails.

00:30:34.170 --> 00:30:35.030 line:80%
But

00:30:35.780 --> 00:30:36.780 line:80%
I have the Night Orchid.

00:30:37.050 --> 00:30:37.890 line:80%
What?

00:30:38.090 --> 00:30:39.460 line:80%
It's not that.

00:30:39.460 --> 00:30:40.740 line:80%
I have a little left.

00:30:40.740 --> 00:30:41.780 line:80%
I gave it to Uncle...

00:30:41.780 --> 00:30:42.620 line:80%
They're here.

00:30:43.460 --> 00:30:44.300 line:80%
They're here!

00:30:50.090 --> 00:30:50.930 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:30:51.180 --> 00:30:53.090 line:80%
leave with the Abbess and Xingjia.

00:30:53.090 --> 00:30:53.930 line:80%
I'll cover.

00:30:54.340 --> 00:30:55.180 line:80%
You go.

00:30:55.180 --> 00:30:56.290 line:80%
Xingjia is badly injured.

00:30:56.290 --> 00:30:57.420 line:80%
I can't carry him.

00:30:57.420 --> 00:30:58.260 line:80%
Go.

00:30:59.780 --> 00:31:00.740 line:80%
Zhao...

00:31:00.740 --> 00:31:01.850 line:80%
Don't worry, Abbess.

00:31:02.500 --> 00:31:03.810 line:80%
I was raised by my aunt.

00:31:22.420 --> 00:31:23.260 line:80%
Cai Zhao!

00:31:23.940 --> 00:31:25.130 line:80%
You demoness!

00:31:26.610 --> 00:31:28.700 line:80%
You repeatedly ruined my plans.

00:31:29.020 --> 00:31:30.940 line:80%
Today, you're mine.

00:31:34.940 --> 00:31:36.130 line:80%
Seize her for me!

00:31:46.700 --> 00:31:48.370 line:80%
The Ziwei Method is powerful.

00:32:06.370 --> 00:32:07.210 line:80%
Stop chasing.

00:32:35.460 --> 00:32:36.330 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:32:37.980 --> 00:32:38.820 line:80%
Go!

00:32:39.050 --> 00:32:39.890 line:80%
Chase!

00:32:46.890 --> 00:32:48.850 line:80%
Mu Qingyan, get down here!

00:32:48.850 --> 00:32:50.530 line:80%
You coward!

00:32:50.530 --> 00:32:51.420 line:80%
Mr. Yu.

00:33:03.810 --> 00:33:04.650 line:80%
You didn't die.

00:33:05.130 --> 00:33:05.980 line:80%
Surprised?

00:33:09.610 --> 00:33:10.660 line:80%
What a relief.

00:33:13.370 --> 00:33:15.500 line:80%
Do you know how much I missed you

00:33:15.940 --> 00:33:17.940 line:80%
and how much I regret what I did?

00:33:20.180 --> 00:33:21.940 line:80%
Fengge, forgive me.

00:33:21.940 --> 00:33:23.330 line:80%
Do you really regret it?

00:33:23.850 --> 00:33:25.130 line:80%
Yes.

00:33:32.890 --> 00:33:33.810 line:80%
Fengge,

00:33:34.700 --> 00:33:36.330 line:80%
you're back now.

00:33:46.180 --> 00:33:47.130 line:80%
Why?

00:33:57.500 --> 00:33:58.370 line:80%
We

00:33:59.850 --> 00:34:00.980 line:80%
are even.

00:34:13.060 --> 00:34:13.900 line:80%
Zhao!

00:34:15.540 --> 00:34:16.380 line:80%
Zhao!

00:34:18.540 --> 00:34:19.380 line:80%
Zhao!

00:34:34.240 --> 00:34:35.100 line:80%
Young Master,

00:34:35.100 --> 00:34:37.450 line:80%
stop sending inner power to Miss Cai,

00:34:37.450 --> 00:34:39.450 line:80%
or you'll die.

00:34:46.780 --> 00:34:47.620 line:80%
Young Master,

00:34:47.620 --> 00:34:48.460 line:80%
this...

00:34:50.180 --> 00:34:51.330 line:80%
If she dies,

00:34:52.890 --> 00:34:54.330 line:80%
what do you think I'll do?

00:35:06.810 --> 00:35:07.650 line:80%
Zhao,

00:35:10.410 --> 00:35:11.930 line:80%
it will soon be over.

00:35:44.780 --> 00:35:45.620 line:80%
Zhao.

00:35:46.100 --> 00:35:46.940 line:80%
Zhao?

00:35:53.140 --> 00:35:54.370 line:80%
You've slept for days.

00:35:55.330 --> 00:35:56.450 line:80%
If I hadn't come,

00:35:58.330 --> 00:35:59.370 line:80%
you would be dead.

00:36:09.540 --> 00:36:11.140 line:80%
That man in black is strong.

00:36:12.290 --> 00:36:13.540 line:80%
How did you escape?

00:36:14.410 --> 00:36:15.490 line:80%
I have my ways.

00:36:17.970 --> 00:36:18.810 line:80%
Here.

00:36:19.410 --> 00:36:20.250 line:80%
Take medicine.

00:36:38.970 --> 00:36:40.100 line:80%
Smiley.

00:36:40.930 --> 00:36:41.850 line:80%
Not as good as yours.

00:36:42.660 --> 00:36:43.540 line:80%
Just make do.

00:36:57.290 --> 00:36:58.130 line:80%
Zhao,

00:37:00.850 --> 00:37:02.780 line:80%
the man in black

00:37:04.890 --> 00:37:06.100 line:80%
feels like someone I know.

00:37:10.841 --> 00:37:21.501 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:37:40.261 --> 00:37:44.671 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:37:45.236 --> 00:37:49.851 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:37:50.191 --> 00:37:54.756 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:37:55.281 --> 00:37:59.581 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:38:02.526 --> 00:38:07.226 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:07.751 --> 00:38:12.041 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:38:12.701 --> 00:38:16.731 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:38:17.046 --> 00:38:22.171 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:38:22.746 --> 00:38:27.556 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:27.771 --> 00:38:31.941 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:38:32.666 --> 00:38:36.601 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:38:37.101 --> 00:38:42.376 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:39:05.106 --> 00:39:10.236 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:10.601 --> 00:39:14.971 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:15.236 --> 00:39:19.366 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:19.551 --> 00:39:25.126 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪